# ===========================================
# OPTIMIZATION NOTES
# ===========================================
# This configuration reduces token usage by:
# - Excluding build artifacts and dependencies
# - Filtering out large data files
# - Removing old/archive documentation
# - Focusing on source code and current documentation
# - Excluding Storybook build files
# - Excluding npm package files
# 
# Expected token reduction: 50-70%
# Expected performance improvement: 20-30%

